{"tid":1153565,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★美股急挫逾650點　騰訊ADR重挫近半成","createTime":"2019-05-13T16:59:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T17:09:48.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6b7ed5d8f92142d181aa3713b0a31d353854e567","tid":1153565,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T16:59:11.000Z","msg":"美股中段愈跌愈急，道指最新報25,284點，跌655點或2.53%；標指最新報2,807點，跌74點或2.57%；納指最新報7,650點，跌266點或3.36%。<br />\n<br />\n港股ADR表現承壓，按比例計算，現報27,831點，跌715點或2.51%。滙豐控股ADR折合報66.09港元，較港收市跌1.21%；騰訊控股ADR折合報363.19元，較港收市跌4.92%。<br />\n<br />\n美國提高對2,000億美元中國貨的關稅後，中方周一(13日)作出反制。中國國務院關稅稅則委員會宣布，今年6月1日起對600億美元、合共5,140項美國貨的加徵關稅，稅率由原來的5%至10%，提高至最多25%。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普此前再於社交網連發多文談及貿易戰，聲稱兩國本已接近達成協議，但中國反口，警告中國不應採取反制措施，否則其經濟形勢會更差。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190514/bkn-20190514005222729-0514_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190514%2Fbkn-20190514005222729-0514_00842_001.html&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHTxn9kyGvuUmJUtyTBy059fc%3D&h=c3ed407e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190514/bkn-20190514005222729-0514_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8bdc655beb61dd5be0ed268b8def33fd7b02c3bc","tid":1153565,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T16:59:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebff9a8bca7279a35479f6771aacac196668964a","tid":1153565,"uid":19932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T17:08:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af58ba04a92673adad55e0d8ede21550ec5a7231","tid":1153565,"uid":166947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T17:08:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agre